The Smart Contact Manager project, developed using Java and Spring Boot, features contact creation, updating, deletion, and cloud storage. It includes user authentication and a responsive design for accessibility across devices. Key technologies involve Maven for build automation, Thymeleaf for dynamic web pages, and Spring Security for secure access. The project uses Hibernate/JPA for database management and integrates RESTful web services for API creation. It emphasizes best practices in version control, unit testing, and continuous integration/deployment, providing a comprehensive full-stack development learning experience.
